column5: Has the water come up any from last years levels? Is it below or above normal for this time of year?
Has the water come up any from last years levels? Is it below or above normal for this time of year?

Hi Fordman, It's at about normal right now. The ice has just left the last of the deep lakes and all is open now. Rain is forcasted so I expect it to remain at a normal stage for the opener. Roger Mayer.
